'''加贺谷千夏'''是日本的'''《[[eXceed]]》'''系列弹幕游戏及其衍生作品的登场角色之一。

==简介==
《[[eXceed-GUN BULLET CHILDREN-]]》与《eXceed 2nd-VAMPIRE-》的登场角色。

==事迹==

《eXceed-GUN BULLET CHILDREN-》中的三自机之一，《eXceed 2nd-VAMPIRE-》及《eXceed 2nd-VAMPIRE REX-》 中的二面BOSS。

===[[eXceed-GUN BULLET CHILDREN-]]===

{{Hide
|标题=英文原文
|内容=
Chinatsu has a complex about her vampiric appearance, which is probably the reason for her aggressive and volatile personality.

She is able to convert magical energy into an ‘Ingzeks’ attack that covers a wide area, giving enemies no opportunity for attack.
<ref>exceed-gbc人物官方介绍页[http://exceedseries.com/exceed-gbc_main/chrs_gb]</ref>
}}

千夏有着关于她吸血鬼的外貌有着复杂一面，那或许是好斗与暴力的性格。

她能够将魔力转化为‘Ingzeks’攻击可以覆盖很广的范围，而她的敌人没有机会攻击。

===[[eXceed 2nd-VAMPIRE-]]===

{{Hide
|标题=英文原文
|内容=
One of the Church’s Gun Bullet Children

Chinatsu wields the magically folded and hardened sword ‘Ingzeks’ and doesn’t hesitate to use it to carve apart any enemy that dares stand before her.

She has a gruff and savage personality, and has no time for small talk.
<ref>[http://exceedseries.com/2nd-vampire-rex/chrs_2vr]</ref>
}}
教会的枪弹少女（Gun Bullet Children）之一。

她使用魔法折叠和硬化的剑“Ingzeks”和毫不犹豫将胆敢站在她面前的敌人切开。

她有着粗暴和野蛮的性格，从不给人闲谈时间。


==她的弹幕==

Grave Hunt  死亡狩猎
